(defxdoc acl2-pc::fancy-use
  :parents (proof-builder-commands)
  :short "(macro)
Use one or more previously-proved theorems efficiently."
  :long "@({
 Examples:
 (fancy-use (:instance my-thm (x a) (y b))
            (disable h))
 (fancy-use (foo (:instance bar (x a))))

 Example of typical usage:
 (defun f2 (x)
   (declare
    (xargs :hints
           ((\"Goal\"
             :instructions
             ((fancy-use ((:instance my-thm (x a) (y b)))
